headline: Is Autodesk Stock Still Attractive Around $300 After Recent Choppy Trading?
summary: Wondering if Autodesk is still worth buying at around $300 a share, or if the big gains are already behind it? This breakdown is designed to help you decide with a cool head rather than a hot headline. Despite a strong roughly 50% gain over the last 3 years, the stock has been choppy lately, down about 2.3% over the last week and roughly flat over the last month, with a modest 2.3% rise year to date and a slight 2.4% dip over the past year. Recent moves have been shaped by ongoing excitement...

headline: Starboard Cuts Match Group Stake Amid Shifting Trends Across Tinder and Hinge
summary: Starboard’s exit highlights a deeper shift at Match Group—one that begins with Tinder’s slowdown but ultimately centers on how the company turns engagement into cash.
